vailable on the first floor of the four story parking structure parking structure 1 at this intersection parking after parking in parking structure 1 cross roth way at the north south mall pass the first two structures on your left keck science and liquid nitrogen storage tank and then turn left walk about 50 feet down this path and you will encounter the swain library which is located in a one story pinkish tan cement block structure the library entrance is on the south west side of the building metered parking is available in parking structure 1 and along lomita drive if you are going to be on campus for several hours you may want to purchase a one day parking permit see stanford university visitor parking which also contains information on parking for visitors with disabilities maps stanford campus searchable stanford libraries visitor information maps and directions transportation and parking maps chemistry and chemical engineering toxicology and chemical safety group menu back stanford university stanford california 94305 650 725 1064 terms of use copyright complaints
